{
  "stem": "6878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started to arrest, mostly, the men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were hiding out like I when-- when they used to come and I used to hide in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to come in, the Germans, and look for men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my wife Ida was then pregnant, and they had sympathy to hear that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When she used to go out, and she used to go out shopping, she used to come with some bread, or this or that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, we were living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The ghetto was locked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were living-- we were 36,000 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the daily problem started in the, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By going to ghetto, they took away all our clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Whatever we carry of clothing, we had to cross a bridge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To go to Kovna, to the Slobodka ghetto, we had to cross a bridge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on that bridge used to be police, mostly Lithuanian, and they used to take away from us the suitcases, everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We went into the ghetto, we were-- whatever we had on ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some managed to get through a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like, I managed a little bit to get through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But most of it were taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And things went on very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Ten days later, when we were locked up, we got a job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They came to the [NON-ENGLISH], which it was the Work Bureau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the German demanded 10, 10 people, electrician, a plumber, and some eight ordinary, without any.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was an electrician, so I had the job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And a plumber was also, by the name [INAUDIBLE], his name was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the job was in a brothel, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Unbelievable, but it was quite reasonable there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were 35 girls, Polish, Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
